Class ServiceSchemaUpgradeWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.ServiceSchemaUpgradeWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ServiceSchemaUpgradeWrapper
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class provides a wrapper for how the attributes within a specific service has changed and defines how said attributes will be upgraded.
